---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="10-Point Checklist for Parents: Choosing a Girls PG in Sambhajinagar"
  description="Before finalising a girls PG in Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, use this 10-point checklist. Covers safety, pricing, food, proximity to Deogiri College and coaching centres."
>
  <section style="padding: 60px 0 80px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Parent guide · 2025</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading" style="max-width:700px;">10-point checklist for parents choosing a girls PG in Sambhajinagar</h1>
      <div class="article-layout">
        <article class="article-body">
          <p>Choosing the right PG accommodation for your daughter in Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar is a decision that affects her safety, academic performance, and overall wellbeing for months or years. This checklist distils the most important factors parents should evaluate before finalising any PG — whether near Deogiri College, DIEMS, Osmanpura coaching hubs, or elsewhere in the city.</p>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Female warden on-site 24x7</h3>
              <p>A female warden who lives on the premises — not just visits — is the single most important safety factor. Ask whether the warden is resident or visiting, and what her shift schedule is.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3>CCTV in all common areas</h3>
              <p>CCTV cameras in corridors, stairwells, the entrance, and common rooms are non-negotiable. Ask to see the footage interface during your visit to verify it is live and recorded.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Walking distance from college or coaching</h3>
              <p>A PG within 1 km of your daughter's college or coaching institute saves 30–60 minutes daily, reduces transport costs, and eliminates late-night travel risk. Jyoti Girls PG is 0.8 km from Deogiri College.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Transparent, all-inclusive pricing</h3>
              <p>Ask for a written breakdown of what is included. Hidden charges for electricity, laundry, or maintenance are common. Jyoti Girls PG charges ₹2,999–₹5,000/month with no hidden fees.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">5</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Proper beds — no bunk beds</h3>
              <p>Bunk beds signal overcrowding and poor sleep hygiene. Verify that the PG provides proper single beds, a personal wardrobe, and a study desk for each resident.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">6</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Power backup and high-speed Wi-Fi</h3>
              <p>Frequent power cuts and slow internet directly impact study quality. Confirm 24x7 power backup and ask for the Wi-Fi speed and router setup before deciding.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">7</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Clear visitor and curfew policy</h3>
              <p>A written curfew policy with defined timings, visitor log, and guardian notification system protects your daughter. Ask for the policy document during your visit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">8</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Parent communication system</h3>
              <p>The PG should have a mechanism to notify parents of late arrivals, illness, or any unusual events. Regular weekly updates — even brief ones — are a sign of professional management.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">9</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Hygienic washrooms and common areas</h3>
              <p>Visit during a weekday, not just on a scheduled tour. Inspect washrooms, the kitchen area (if meals are served), and the passageways. Daily cleaning logs should be visible.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="checklist-item">
            <div class="checklist-num">10</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Talk to current residents and parents</h3>
              <p>Ask the PG management for references. A credible PG will connect you with current residents or their parents who are willing to share their experience. Jyoti Girls PG provides references on request.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2>How Jyoti Girls PG scores on this checklist</h2>
          <p>Jyoti Girls PG in Jyoti Nagar, Osmanpura fulfils all 10 points. Our resident female warden is on-site 24x7, CCTV covers all common areas, we are 0.8 km from Deogiri College, pricing starts at ₹2,999/month with no hidden charges, all rooms have proper single beds, power backup and Wi-Fi are uninterrupted, and we maintain a documented visitor and curfew policy.</p>
          <p>We welcome parent visits on any weekday. Call or WhatsApp us to schedule a walkthrough before you finalise your decision.</p>
        </article>
        <aside class="article-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Jyoti Girls PG scores 10/10</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-price">₹2,999<span style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">/mo</span></div>
            <p class="sidebar-note">Osmanpura · 0.8 km from Deogiri College</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305" class="btn-primary" style="display:block;text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;">WhatsApp to book</a>
            <a href="tel:+919922333305" class="btn-outline" style="display:block;text-align:center;">Call us</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
